45:04.005 --> 45:05.920
but I-I never cared
about dinner.

45:05.964 --> 45:08.575
I was just pissed
he never let me do it.

45:10.185 --> 45:12.405
You want in?

45:12.448 --> 45:15.016
Yeah.

